| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0390 — Recovery Inhibition (darkvault)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 263b9aca-f6af-54df-8e82-e1552e69616f"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
